      "There be giants, ogres and trolls near Trinsic ... and pirates in the waters.",
      "Trinsic? 'Tis the land's guardian, a city that teaches paladins the ways of honor and virtue.",
      "'Tis a place of swift justice, is Trinsic. Thieves are as rare as whistling cats."
    }
#Key "*okllo*" "*ocllo*" {
      "Ocllo? Doubt I heard of it.",
      "Ocllo? Island folks, I think.",
      "I've no ken of Ocllo.",
      "Ocllo ... hmmm. 'Tis an island, I believe.",
      "Ocllo ... rings a bell. Mayhaps something to do with salt ....",
      "Ocllo? Sounds very like the beginning of a joke!"
    }
